<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container-fluid flex-wrapper-main index-container">
  <div class="row header-row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6  header-side-text">
      <h2>Welcome!</h2>
      <h4>The world is changing before your eyes <br>
        And it will not wait for you <br>
        We teach you how to be successful in it</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 carousel-container index-section">
      <div id="carouselCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <div class="card">
              <img src="./<%-newsArray[0].image %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><%-newsArray[0].title %></h5>
                <p class="card-text"><%-newsArray[0].description %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% for (let i=1 ; i<newsArray.length ; i++) {%>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="card">
              <img src="./<%-newsArray[i].image %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><%-newsArray[i].title %></h5>
                <% if (newsArray[i].description.length <= 140) { %>
                <p class="card-text"><%-newsArray[i].description %></p>
                <% } else { %>
                <p class="card-text"><%-newsArray[i].description.slice(0,140) + "..." %></p>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12  header-side-text">
      <h2>The world is undergoing a paradigm shift at a rapid pace and traditional education cannot
        keep up</h2>
      <h4>We live in a world where confidence in traditional education is at an all-time low. Higher
        education is a debt trap that is behind the times, leaving people without the tools they need to
        succeed in a rapidly changing world with a new set of rules. Many people will be left behind in the
        greatest transfer of wealth in human history. You do not have to be one of them. DeGen University
        has you covered.</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 header-side-text">
      <h2>Get the tools you need to find your way to excellence. Equal Opportunity, Unequal Results</h2>
      <h4>With our free courses aimed at levelling the playing field for everyone. You'll learn the basics
        of cryptocurrency, DeFI, ecommerce, fitness and more. No magic pills. No gurus. </h4>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" name="button">I want to learn</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 index-img">
      <img src="/images/DEGEN_ANIMALS.png" alt="degen-animals-img">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row header-row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 header-side-text">
      <h2>Meet our professors</h2>
      <h4>In DeGen University we select the most elite people in their fields. Would you like to find
        them? Want to learn more about them? Find all their information and social media in just 2 clicks. </h4>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" name="button">I want to know them</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 index-img">
      <img src="/images/CLASS_IN_SESSION.png" alt="class-in-session-img">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 header-side-text">
      <h2>Show your support for us!</h2>
      <h4>Browse DeGen University's exclusive merch and our professors' products! With every
        purchase, you help our professors provide you with more and better education.</h4>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" name="button">Click here</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 index-img">
      <img src="/images/OX_SHOPPING_CART.png" alt="shopping-cart-img">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
